title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 7 2022
description:
Dems put on Hamilton musical performance at Jan. 6th memorial. Clay's advice instead, as he also always gives to his kids: JBN -- Just Be Normal, don't do strange grand gestures. There will be no normalcy until all schools are open. Dr. Marty Makary joins Clay and Buck to discuss the latest on Omicron, which he calls Omicold. C&B parody: Mask Anxiety Disorder, MAD.
